oofem.out
Reinforced prism
NonLinearStatic nmsteps 1 nsteps 1 profileopt 1 nmodules 1 contextOutputStep 1000
nsteps 1 rtolf 1.e-3 stiffMode 2 maxiter 1000 controllmode 1 donotfixload
vtkxmllattice primvars 1 1 cellvars 4 46 60 90 111 tstep_all domain_all cross 1
domain 3d
OutputManager tstep_step 1 dofman_output { 5 }
ncrosssect 1 nmat 1 nbc 1 nic 0 nltf 2 nset 1 
